      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stéphane Nguyen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"/File:St%C3%A9phaneNguyen.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/0/0b/St%C3%A9phaneNguyen.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"182\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:St%C3%A9phaneNguyen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stéphane Nguyen <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stéphane Nguyen</b>,<br />\na French computer chess programmer and author of the <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> chess engine <a href=\"/Jester\" title=\"Jester\">Jester</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nStéphane participated with Jester at multiple <a href=\"/French_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"French Computer Chess Championship\">French Computer Chess Championships</a> and <a href=\"/French_Programmers_Tournament\" title=\"French Programmers Tournament\">French Programmers Tournaments</a>, and maintained a Computer Chess Site, also reporting on the tournaments.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=St%C3%A9phane_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20121030040515/http://www.ludochess.com/dotcom/accueil.php3\">Ludochess.com</a> - Stéphane Nguyen's Computer Chess Site (French) (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=St%C3%A9phane_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Stéphane Nguyen at <a href=\"/FCCC_2002\" title=\"FCCC 2002\">FCCC 2002</a>, Image cropped from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20090419012000/http://www.ludochess.com/fccc2002/tournoi.php3\">Massy, France - 5 &amp; 6 Oct 2002 - 9ème Championnat Français de Programmes d'Echecs</a>, Other pictures from <a href=\"/Sylvain_Renard\" title=\"Sylvain Renard\">Sylvain</a>: <a href=\"/Eric_Marath%C3%A9e\" title=\"Eric Marathée\">Eric Marathée</a>, <a href=\"/Franck_Zibi\" title=\"Franck Zibi\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stéphane Nguyen</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070329055806/http://www.ludochess.com/jester_eng/jester_eng.php3\">JESTER, the strongest pure java chess program</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301082305\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 